title: Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate | whitehouse.gov

The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
April 15, 2015

 



Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate




NOMINATIONS SENT TO THE SENATE:
Linda Struyk Millsaps, of North Carolina, to be a Member of the Internal Revenue Service Oversight Board for a term expiring September 14, 2018, vice Paul Jones, term expired.
Thomas Edgar Rothman, of Maryland, to be a Member of the National Council on the Arts for a term expiring September 3, 2016.Â  (New Position)
